# 7. Reverse Each Word in Sentence

## Solution

```python
s = "hello world"

words = s.split()

for word in words:

    reverse = ""

    for ch in word:
        reverse = ch + reverse

    print(reverse, end=" ")
```

## Output

```text
olleh dlrow
```

