# 9. Character Compression Logic

## Solution

```python
s = "aaabbcccc"

count = 1

for i in range(len(s)-1):

    if s[i] == s[i+1]:
        count += 1

    else:
        print(s[i] + str(count), end="")
        count = 1

print(s[-1] + str(count))
```

## Output

```text
a3b2c4
```

